          practice: "In Packet Tracer: configure OSPF on a serial link between R1 and R2. Run 'show ip ospf interface Se0/0/0' and note 'Network Type POINT_TO_POINT' and 'No designated router.' Run 'show ip ospf neighbor' and note FULL/ - state. Compare with an Ethernet link between the same routers (broadcast by default, DR elected).",
